Barclays Bank is a global universal bank, offering retail, private, corporate 
and investment banking products and services worldwide. Barclays bank plc operates as a branch of Barclays Bank plc (United Kingdom).  Barclays bank plc is rated by Moody's. Long-term credit rating assigned to the bank by Moody's is A2  (upper medium grade).  Barclays bank plc participates in deposit guarantee scheme of the United Kingdom. 
This scheme covers accounts up to 85 000 GBP per bank per depositor.  Barclays bank plc is located in PARIS 08.




Address32 AVENUE GEORGE V, 75008, PARIS 08, France 

Member of Group Barclays (United Kingdom)HeadquartersBarclays Bank plc (United Kingdom)Bank CategoryBranches of foreign banks  
 


 

