Barclays Corporate – Provides banking solutions to organisations with an annual turnover of more than £5 million, including Deposits and Liquidity, Cash Management and Trade, Financing, Foreign Exchange, Risk Management and Online Banking.[103] It serves over 8,000 companies across 23 countries.[103]
Barclays Croatia
