Barclays Bank PLC: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















barclays bank plc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Banking
Sub-Industry: Banks
Barclays Bank PLC is a diversified banking and financial services group. The Groups principal activities include retail and corporate banking, investment banking, treasury services, consumer finance, and insurance. Barclays Bank serves clients worldwide.




