Ways to find barclays bank plc france swift code or BIC code are many but this is the most effective way to do the job. For barclays bank plc france, located at 32 avenue george v, you will be using BIC / Swift code BARCFRPP. You can also find and check BIC/Swift code for barclays bank plc france without any hesitation. Feel free to verify the swift code against our database.  The formation of SWIFT or Society for Worldwide Interbank Financial Telecommunication Code has made the process of transferring money very simple. Now you or anyone else can send money oversees without any kind of hesitation because it is a safe and secure way for making an international wire transfer. The role of SWIFT code cannot be ignored when it comes to international wire transfer.



